author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-B2holding ‍Q4 Operating Profit Rises To NOK 301 Million​
text:
Feb 28 (Reuters) - B2HOLDING ASA:
* ‍BOARD PROPOSES TO AGM TO APPROVE A DIVIDEND OF NOK 0.30 PER SHARE.​
* Q4 ‍GROSS CASH COLLECTION OF NOK 723 MILLION (556) - UP 30% Y-O-Y​
* Q4 ‍OPERATING PROFIT OF NOK 301 MILLION (151) - UP 99% Y-O-Y​
* ‍Q4 CASH EBITDA OF NOK 524 MILLION (349) - UP 50% Y-O-Y​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
